ğŸ“– Simple Linear Regression
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

A simple Linear Regression practice in Python to predict student marks based on hours studied.  
This is purely a **practice exercise** to understand basic machine learning concepts.

â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
â„¹ï¸  Overview
â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

â€¢ Load and explore the dataset (`hrs_marks.csv`)  
â€¢ Visualize Hours Studied vs Marks  
â€¢ Train a Linear Regression model  
â€¢ Predict marks for new study hours  
â€¢ Plot the regression line for interpretation  

â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
